<span id="freeTextContainer49555065665406218">A tightly woven and gritty police procedural set in New Orleans. Really enjoyed the main character Dave Robicheaux and will no doubt go on to read more in the series. Robicheaux was a deeply flawed character, plagued by inner demons but had integrity and perseverance.<br/><br/>The mystery component was well delivered I didn&apos;t realise how it would all play out and that&apos;s always a plus. Loved the setting and descriptions of a lush and humid New Orleans. Well worth a look at.</span>
