<div id="review_1304568701" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1304568701" />
    <a title="Wayne Barrett" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/21372390-wayne-barrett"><img alt="Wayne Barrett" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1625178759p2/21372390.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1304568701?book_show_action=true">Mar 19, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Wayne Barrett" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Wayne Barrett" href="/user/show/21372390-wayne-barrett">Wayne Barrett</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback " href="/book/show/867097.The_Neon_Rain">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/21372390-wayne-barrett?shelf=thriller">thriller</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/21372390-wayne-barrett?shelf=mystery">mystery</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/21372390-wayne-barrett?shelf=southern-gothic">southern-gothic</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/21372390-wayne-barrett?shelf=2017">2017</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/21372390-wayne-barrett?shelf=crime">crime</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/21372390-wayne-barrett?shelf=series">series</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1304568701" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8336064519869182122"><br/>4.5<br/><br/>This is hardcore crime at its best. Detective Dave Robicheaux is one of the good guys at heart, an officer that still believes in justice and the welfare of others, but he is also one bad, bad dude, and if he has to bend the laws a little to bring about justice you better not get in his way.<br/><br/>The only chink in the armor of this novel is that Daves toughness at times crossed the line into what I can only call stupidity... but hey, he&apos;s only human, and I would damn sure never say it to his face. </span>
  <span id="freeText8336064519869182122" style="display:none"><br />4.5<br /><br />This is hardcore crime at its best. Detective Dave Robicheaux is one of the good guys at heart, an officer that still believes in justice and the welfare of others, but he is also one bad, bad dude, and if he has to bend the laws a little to bring about justice you better not get in his way.<br /><br />The only chink in the armor of this novel is that Daves toughness at times crossed the line into what I can only call stupidity... but hey, he's only human, and I would damn sure never say it to his face. <br /><br />I will certainly be checking out more of this series. </span>
