<span id="freeTextContainer15697677720073092180"><strong>The Neon Rain</strong><br/><br/>This is the first James Lee Burke novel I&apos;ve read in a very long time. I decided to start at the beginning and re-read all of his novels in order and with this first book I&apos;m not disappointed. I can&apos;t wait to start the next book in the Dave Robicheaux series. </span>
  <span id="freeText15697677720073092180" style="display:none"><strong>The Neon Rain</strong><br /><br />This is the first James Lee Burke novel I've read in a very long time. I decided to start at the beginning and re-read all of his novels in order and with this first book I'm not disappointed. I can't wait to start the next book in the Dave Robicheaux series. </span>
